      >
        Saurav Sidharthan
      </h2>
      <h3
        style="--order: 7;"
        style="word-spacing: -10px;"
        class="sm:text-5xl text-2xl mb-6 slide-in-hidden"
      >
        I build web3 apps for a decentralized world! ðŸš€
